{"tid":127703,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"空姐露奶照粉香豔　網友喊滿足制服情結","createTime":"2017-02-20T09:36:34.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-20T10:20:54.000Z","uid":58791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a2f42bef4db7917fad7fcc0456c83ff6e5fdceab","tid":127703,"uid":58791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T09:36:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BN0AFEr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBN0AFEr.jpg&h=58394df6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n現代女孩思想開放，有好身材都不吝與大家分享，更愛穿著工作服裝拍「豔光四射」的照片，日前就有「香港航空」的空姐，穿制服大秀身材的照片被網傳。<br />\n這位香港航空的空姐自拍，輕解制服鈕扣到胸部下、露出白色蕾絲胸罩、豐滿北半球與事業線，巧笑倩兮的照片。消息中說，她的動作與神態都相當誘人，有網友高呼「完全滿足了我的制服情結」！不過，也有網友表示，基於尊重專業形象，空姐想露奶時，還是不要穿制服比較好。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/new/20170219/1059910\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.appledaily.com.tw%2Frealtimenews%2Farticle%2Fnew%2F20170219%2F1059910&d=Mrz8gheyF4cbCiJyPb%2FMEzCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=02b63482\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/new/20170219/1059910</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有無巴打有多D圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56e98f6aaf0ffa5aed6ea9ae8526aa99aff98e73","tid":127703,"uid":60569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T09:43:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4aabf8b0770acb2ea6f703acdfb22d6237755444","tid":127703,"uid":39551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T09:45:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/as